<center><table border=0><tr><td><center><H2><font face=arial>Roleplaying a pvp</font></H2></center>
<font face=arial size=2><b>Posted By:</b> <A HREF="/cgi-local/whois2.cgi?Bragador">Bragador</a><br>
<b>Posted On:</b> 10:08 a.m. 21/11/1999<br>
<b>Subject:</b> Roleplaying a pvp<p>
<br><center><img src="http://www.everworld.net/pvpquest/images/divider.gif" width=452 height=22 border=0></center><BR></STRONG><FONT SIZE=2 color=#FFFFFF FACE=arial>
<P>Hi,

<BR>I just want to say that pvp is a must in a virtual world like everquest. Without pvp, there would be no bounty hunters, no criminals that attack the road travellers, etc. AND there would be no raid against cities!
<BR>The problem is that some pk can't roleplay a fun caracter and they just run around trying to kill evreyone that can't resist their wrath. Those are missing a great part of the game. And i'm no talking about those who wait next to the corpses of their victims to kill them 3-4 times.
<BR>I would like that we, fellow pk, starts a new way of playing, the way of the futur. Let us live our caracter without having to encounter serial killers every 5 minutes. Show the example and roleplay your caracter(by roleplaying I don't mean speaking in old english, i'm speaking about acting in a realistic way).
<BR>Remember this: pkilling is not a excuse to make everquest a huge brawling game, it's suppose to add realism. Instead of saying hail to whoever you meet, pkilling makes us act in a realistic manner saying : stop! who's there? what do you want?.
<BR>I hope someday pkilling will be realistic and not like what it is today.
<BR>Because saying that some races, or even some classes are not appropriate for a pk world is a very very very sad proof that the fun of being a pk is reducing. IT IS NOT A COMBAT ARENA, IT'S AN ADVENTURE GAME WITH EVIL CARACTERS IN IT. (by the way, don't forget you can be a pk AND a good caracter ex:shadow knight vs paladin)
<P>SO roleplay, don't kill everyone you see.
<P>Bragador
</FONT></td></tr></table></P>
